'''Akallabeth MUSH''' is a [[wikipedia:MUSH|MUSH]] set in [[Middle-earth]] during {{SA}} 3179.<ref name="Tolkien Games">[http://www.lysator.liu.se/tolkien-games/entry/akallabeth.html Akallabeth MUSH] at Tolkien Games (retrieved 15 April 2011)</ref><ref name="Review">[http://haven.theonering.net/reviews/games/akallabeth.html Review] (retrieved 15 April 2011)</ref> There are four races:<ref name="Review"/>

* [[High Elves|An Elf]] under the kingship of [[Gil-galad]]
* [[Númenóreans|A Númenoréan]], both man and woman.
* [[Orcs|An Orc]] from [[Mordor]].
* [[Hill-men|A Hillman]].
